<br>
This games looks so much like Diablo in some aspects... my dictionnary says that the word for this is &quot;plagiarism&quot;. The main difference is: Diablo was dull and DS is very exiting!<br>
<br>
The interface is very nice, just start the game and everything is just in the right place and easy to understand without having to read the manuel.<br>
<br>
The sound track really gets you in the game. What's that song in chapter 1? I know it from somewhere... is it Vangelis in charriots of fire? Not sure, but its not an original composition as it is stated in the credits! (plagiarism again?)<br>
<br>
Having control over a 8 character party is pretty nice too. You can hire a healer for 900 gold and he will follow you everywhere without ever getting lost! (ducks from Krystl!) <br>
<br>
On the other hand, his conversation is pretty dull and even with an 8 character party, I would feel pretty lonely playing this.<br>
What will you be playing this autumn? Will DoAC still be the game? Or is it NWN that will capture all your attention? AC 2? <br>
